    "Real-time monitoring of PM.",
    "concentrations in the individually exposed participants was carried out.",
    "Data on individual characteristics, heart rate (HR), blood pressure (BP), and lung function at baseline and during the follow-ups were collected.",
    "The effects of PM.",
    "exposure on lung function were assessed within each group using linear mixed-effect models."
